TextEng: Who are you? You are not from Charwood?
Who you be? You not from Charwood?
Text: 너 누구야? 너 그을린숲 사람 아니야?

TextEng: Settle down. What are you talking about?
Ssh! What this you saying?
I don't have time for this. Goodbye.
Me no got time. Goodbye.
I seek a cult responsible for plague in Neverwinter.
Text: 네버윈터에 역병을 일으킨 사교를 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Me hunt cult that bring plague to Neverwinter.
Text: 나 네버윈터에 역병 일으킨 사교 찾아.

TextEng: Who are you?
Who you?
What do you mean I'm not here?
What you mean me not be here?
Text: 나 여기 없다는 게 무슨 뜻이야?

TextEng: What are you looking for?
What you be lookin' for?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can tell me. Maybe I can help.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 말해도 돼. 도와줄 수 있을지도 몰라.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You tell me. Mebbe me help, yuh?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 말해봐. 내가 도와줄 수도 있어, 응?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Look, it's important that you tell me.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Tell me. It important, okay?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Where is the cult based? Who's in charge?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Where da cult be? Who be in charge?
The cult? The one from Neverwinter?
Da cult? From Neverwinter?
